{"tid":1792327,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「做乜趕我走呀？」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-21T14:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T16:28:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb8ed62cf64b6f2a53ffe1a2e1ef5557b0fcf31","tid":1792327,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191218/20826861/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826861%2F&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Az7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=bab1e292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826861%2F&h=c68fc42f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191218/20826861/</a><br />\n<br />\n「做乜趕我走呀？」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191218/large/1576573997_291d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576573997_291d.jpg&h=a7aa1484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2016年震驚全港的荃灣DAN 6工廈石棺藏屍案審結，死者亡魂應得安息，已離開現場吧。<br />\n<br />\n殺人後3被告潛逃台灣，與他們同居的小草當污點證人得特赦，才可破案。但審訊一波三折，先是去年主審官因患病需即時跟進治療，解散全體陪審團。後定今年3月重審，小草懷孕及產後休養，一延再延&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3人用哥羅芳焗死張姓友人，斬開，再用水泥、木板及其他材料製成石棺，藏屍於廁所。因太重無法搬離寓所棄置，只好着草。石棺破開時已嚴重腐爛難辨。今年10月起至今審訊結案，首被告謀殺罪成判囚終身，第二、三被告誤殺成，均需付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n警方完成調查後將單位解封，當時屋內一片凌亂，屋主帶同兩名清潔工人收拾及整理，當打開大門時，廁所內有影子及傳來陰森男聲：「做乜趕我走呀？」屋主呆立當場，只好打發工人，關上大門，安排超渡法事。而這單位直至今年5月才以178萬元（蝕讓110萬元）賤賣離場。<br />\n<br />\n亡魂死得冤，是不能「趕走」的。他或者不知自己已死，又或者在遇害過程中受驚嚇受痛苦，三魂七魄四散，一直戀棧最後的落腳處。超渡的儀式是誦經、勸善、點化，讓他們放下執念和愛恨恩怨，離場，超脫，往生，一路好走，早日投胎轉世，過新生活&hellip;&hellip;這是一種慈悲。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"0e80765a34ed1610214faabf68f28e0da63238c3","tid":1792327,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">聲援維吾爾族人權集會</span><br />\n12.22 星期日 <br />\n時間 : 15:30<br />\n地點 : 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span><br />\n學生歷量<br />\n公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Pk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FPk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Az7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=2fc184c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Pk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw</a>"},{"pid":"39404b8bf32621c71b02afaf3d1dcb85f8683e78","tid":1792327,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"幾錢租"}]}